snippet.title: SPEED KILLS
snippet.description:
Developed by indie dev team Holy Warp, 'SPEED KILLERS' pays homage to all those awesome Genesis (Mega Drive) 16-bit full-on isometric battle racing games.   It's fast, it's furious and it death racing as it should be!!

SPEED KILLS is available in both standalone and Special Edition (featuring the full soundtrack as a music file) formats.
